Titolo: Knightmare (1991 video game)

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Knightmare is a computer game on the Amiga and Atari ST computer systems. It was released in 1991 by Mindscape International Ltd.. The game was written by Tony Crowther. It is based on the Anglia Television TV show Knightmare.
This was the second of two games based on the show, following an earlier game - also known as Knightmare - released four years previously by Activision.